{"tid":467107,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[飛機膠]阿聯酋航空推出全新波音777客艙配置，私密隔間頭等艙最大亮點","createTime":"2017-11-13T08:09:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-20T06:01:57.000Z","uid":64181,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"afbf89fe788cd44ce2725ef5d21e90139367aae4","tid":467107,"uid":64181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T08:09:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.mobile01.com/640x480/attach/201711/mobile01-0be801b7b0f75ea39ef6a7a2f4b4c82d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.mobile01.com%2F640x480%2Fattach%2F201711%2Fmobile01-0be801b7b0f75ea39ef6a7a2f4b4c82d.jpg&h=cd7c71f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n還記得上個星期我們剛介紹的新加坡航空全新空中巴士A380客艙配置嗎？（文章連結：雙人豪華套房飛上天！新加坡航空推出A380全新客艙配置）其中頭等艙雙人套房的設計，讓許多航空迷們驚艷，不過同樣以奢華頭等艙規劃為強項的阿聯酋航空（Emirates），馬上在舉行中的杜拜航空展發表全新波音777客艙設計，咱們一起來看看！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先來看看阿聯酋航空官方提供的影片介紹吧！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/p2hJxyF7mok\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fp2hJxyF7mok&d=%2FYMK0%2FgWmQ5%2F85T3GOZOdUzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=cf7c228d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/p2hJxyF7mok</a>"},{"pid":"8d83a17d9567ea14b74b004688f9ae6e97107919","tid":467107,"uid":64181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T08:10:30.000Z","msg":"看到這照片，可能會以為是頂級私人飛機的內裝配置，其實這正是阿聯酋全新推出的頭等艙套房（Suite）實際配置，設計風格採用源自M.Benz S-Class的內裝概念，以淺色原木飾板、皮革與氣氛燈營造舒適、放鬆的個人空間，座椅也以質地柔軟、觸感極佳的皮革包覆，並可透過電動調整至個人感到最舒適的位置，當然也能完全平躺，並由空服員鋪設成一張舒適的睡床。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.mobile01.com/640x480/attach/201711/mobile01-e3c842347ad474253f960a463eca33b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.mobile01.com%2F640x480%2Fattach%2F201711%2Fmobile01-e3c842347ad474253f960a463eca33b2.jpg&h=8d5936a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全新頭等艙套房的最大亮點，便是採用挑頂式的全覆式隔門設計，上次介紹的新加坡航空A380雙人套房雖然營造了類似飯店高級套房的雙人空間，但隔間拉門仍是半截設計，也就是說空服員或是路過的其他頭等艙旅客還是可以探頭往內看，這次阿聯酋推出的頭等艙套房則具備出色的個人隱密空間，送餐時也可請空服員從獨立規劃的送餐窗口提供服務。"},{"pid":"5f62aa979ac4060b0a81235ddd12a003a1c350fb","tid":467107,"uid":64181,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T08:12:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.mobile01.com/640x480/attach/201711/mobile01-d7cba22b83efea93c6a766c2baddff1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.mobile01.com%2F640x480%2Fattach%2F201711%2Fmobile01-d7cba22b83efea93c6a766c2baddff1f.jpg&h=8bac539b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n這次推出的頭等艙套房採用1-1-1座位配置，每架全新客艙規劃的777客機共有六個頭等艙座位，內部空間為40平方英尺，並配置32吋高解析度液晶螢幕，旅客能以座椅旁的13吋無線控制面板控制娛樂系統或點餐，而在巡航途中也能隨時點餐；此外，頭等艙套房內同樣配置個人Mini bar、電源插座、兩組USB、一組USB Type-C、HDMI插座等，還可獨立控制套房內氣氛燈與獨立空調系統。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.mobile01.com/640x480/attach/201711/mobile01-751d380c3b36625d046fb0f4d51d8c32.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.mobile01.com%2F640x480%2Fattach%2F201711%2Fmobile01-751d380c3b36625d046fb0f4d51d8c32.jpg&h=d61288e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由於座艙配置採用1-1-1規劃，中央的頭等艙套房則設置「虛擬機窗」，能將客機外的即時影像投影於螢幕，同樣能帶來類似坐在靠窗座位的感受。這次推出的全新客艙設計，將從12月1日起首飛杜拜-日內瓦以及杜拜-布魯塞爾航線，未來也將陸續增設歐洲航線，台灣的旅客也不妨考慮嚐鮮。"},{"pid":"31c0a9edb78f5c889fd709e5f4cfc781fd60ccc0","tid":467107,"uid":64181,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T08:15:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.mobile01.com/640x480/attach/201711/mobile01-d276ebcb7433d4d086af111fd3e5a71c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.mobile01.com%2F640x480%2Fattach%2F201711%2Fmobile01-d276ebcb7433d4d086af111fd3e5a71c.jpg&h=51deb384&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在官網查了一下票價，如果從台北前往日內瓦搭乘頭等艙，標準票價約為台幣29.5萬元。（將於杜拜轉機，台北-杜拜航線仍是A380改款前的客艙配置）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.mobile01.com/640x480/attach/201711/mobile01-ce7e09843df5181f7c8138db7634c008.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.mobile01.com%2F640x480%2Fattach%2F201711%2Fmobile01-ce7e09843df5181f7c8138db7634c008.jpg&h=51e04203&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除了頭等艙之外，商務艙以及經濟艙也同時換新裝，其中商務艙採用2-3-2座位配置，椅距為72英寸，座椅同樣具有平躺功能；至於經濟艙則採用3-4-3座位配置，同樣維持高運量的內部規劃，不過商務艙與經濟艙同時升級全新個人娛樂系統，不僅螢幕解析度提升，內部功能也更加齊全"},{"pid":"3b0252ed0ba358c12f376afd64e7f937713308dd","tid":467107,"uid":511,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T08:15:17.000Z","msg":"窮撚只係得過望字<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3908927e4456b3e2cf083b27d3c636ecdeddd0b","tid":467107,"uid":64181,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T08:16:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://attach.mobile01.com/640x480/attach/201711/mobile01-0fb9bf32ee34657f48c785e150542762.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.mobile01.com%2F640x480%2Fattach%2F201711%2Fmobile01-0fb9bf32ee34657f48c785e150542762.jpg&h=ccaafe74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.mobile01.com/640x480/attach/201711/mobile01-792800a12b4ba8e72bcdd2f31a400a11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.mobile01.com%2F640x480%2Fattach%2F201711%2Fmobile01-792800a12b4ba8e72bcdd2f31a400a11.jpg&h=3ead71a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.mobile01.com/640x480/attach/201711/mobile01-2f3eaca72498442ac8267de11ee266eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.mobile01.com%2F640x480%2Fattach%2F201711%2Fmobile01-2f3eaca72498442ac8267de11ee266eb.jpg&h=888df483&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed234ad5ef0352d744186ba8a8aa310eef892ca4","tid":467107,"uid":64181,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T08:16:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>窮撚只係得過望字<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a34093004d1003863755cf18637563f0560e15e7","tid":467107,"uid":16034,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T08:20:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>窮撚只係得過望字<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\